here in the U.S. and offshore in multiple

00:01:33.289 --> 00:01:38.920
countries.
My favorite store of value

00:01:38.920 --> 00:01:42.639
The biggest advantage to holding precious
metals (Gold, Silver, Platinum, &amp; Palladium)

00:01:42.639 --> 00:01:48.139
is that no one really knows you have them.
They are liquid assets outside of the system,

00:01:48.139 --> 00:01:53.049
easily portable, and are rare metals that
have to be mined giving them a real and lasting

00:01:53.049 --> 00:01:57.350
value.
I recommend 5-10% of your net worth in physical

00:01:57.350 --> 00:02:03.709
precious metals, think of gold specifically
like an insurance policy. Many people ask

00:02:03.709 --> 00:02:08.780
me all the time about what the gold price
is going to do next... To me, this is like

00:02:08.780 --> 00:02:13.880
expecting a return on investment from my auto
insurance, healthcare, or ADT alarm system

00:02:13.880 --> 00:02:19.600
